About Ilana

Hello! My name is Ilana! I love Photography, Makeup Artistry and, Social Media!

I am a positive person and I enjoy meeting new people and chatting about anything and everything!

I am college educated with a bachelors degree in Fashion Design & Fine Art and, an associates degree in Photography.

I graduated cum laude from the University of North Texas.

I model on the side but photography is my escape and I love all forms of art.

Enjoy Life! Be Positive and Always Follow Your Dreams!

Love, Ilana
